features: WIDER COVERAGE-ALLOWING WIFI RUN FURTHER: WiFi 6 Extenders Equipped with four external independent FEMs, each of which has signal amplification function (PA) and weak signal enhancement function (LNA), amplify the coverage range of the home signal to 12000 square feet and achieves true WiFi full house coverage.

EFFICIENT TRANSMISSION ACROSS MULTIPLE DEVICES: 2024 internet signal booster with strong combination of MU-MIMO+OFDMA technology. Enjoy smoother and more reliable streaming, gaming, downloading, and more with dual-band WiFi speeds up to 3000Mbps (2400 Mbps on 5 GHz and 574Mbps on 2.4 GHz).

EASY SETUP IN MINUTES: Easily set up in a few quick and easy steps with the WPS button. No need to download APP; users can judge the signal strength of the wireless wifi extender by the color of the indicator light. Create a seamless WiFi network using compatible OneMesh routers and internet booster so you never have to switch networks or lose signal.

SECURE ENCRYPTION: wifi repeater booster Support WPA/WPA2/WPA3 encryption protocol, anti-hacking, anti-hijacking, multiple protection, more secure network. The cooling holes of the body are arranged in an orderly manner, avoiding the aging of parts and unstable operation of the equipment brought about by heat dissipation - a series of problems to ensure the stable operation of the equipment.

GIGABIT ETHERNET PORT: The AX3000 network wifi extender is compatible with all router, Support 128+ Devices, Zero Bog. Experience wired speed and reliability anywhere in your home with the gigabit ethernet port, Pumping out interference-free, lightning-fast data capabilities to all tablets, smart speakers, Alexa devices, IP cameras and whatever the innerwebs invents next.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars If you’re having WIFI range issues, give this a try!
reviews.reviewText: I had tried a few other extenders with far more reviews (e.g., 20 to 100k) — mostly positive — and they still didn’t work for me (some wouldn’t even connect at all). I took a chance on this one that had a low number of reviews, but all absolutely glowing, and boy am I glad I did! My old extender worked ok years, but started to tap out. I have finally found a replacement that works& even better than before :-) Set up was so simple, and I’ve had no issue with lag or timing out so far. Would highly recommend giving this one a try.
